&lt;li&gt;You receive ongoing support: I maintain your site as your business grows — so it never falls behind again&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-website-problems-i-help-fix"&gt;Common Website Problems I Help Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update an outdated website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fix a slow or broken website&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make your website mobile-friendly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve your Google ranking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help with your website when your designer disappears&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get a new website without losing your domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing website updates &amp;amp; content changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Affordable monthly maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="why-businesses-trust-me"&gt;Why Businesses Trust Me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I work directly with business owners to create websites that actually work — not just look good. You won’t get passed off to a big agency or left in the dark. I make sure you keep full control of your domain, your content, and your site. Every website I build is designed to be fast, mobile-friendly, and easy to update as your business grows. And unlike one-time designers who disappear after launch, I stick around to keep your site evolving with you — so you never fall behind again.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Free 30-Min Google Business Profile Audit | Freelance Website Designer for Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/free-google-business-profile-profile-audit/</link><pubDate>Mon, 04 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/free-google-business-profile-profile-audit/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;picture style="display:inline-block; aspect-ratio:1024/1024;"&gt;&lt;source type="image/avif" srcset="https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w320.avif 320w, https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w480.avif 480w, https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w640.avif 640w, https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w768.avif 768w, https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w960.avif 960w, https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w1024.avif 1024w" sizes="100vw"&gt;&lt;img src="https://clearpresence.io/media-deriv/google-business-profile-audit__w1024.jpg"
