&lt;p&gt;Your Google Business Profile is one of your most powerful tools for attracting local customers. But are you using it to its full potential? As a freelance web designer who helps small businesses in Utah, I&amp;rsquo;m offering a free, no-obligation 30-minute video chat to audit your Google Business Profile. Together, we&amp;rsquo;ll identify simple adjustments you can make to get more calls and new business.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Does Google Analytics Slow Down Your Website?</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/does-google-analytics-slow-down-website/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/does-google-analytics-slow-down-website/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Google Analytics is heavy and will slow down your website. I have proven this for myself by going to Page Speed Insights and testing websites with and without analytics. Some sites recommend using the defer attribute on your script but that does not help. Other sites recommend turning off enhanced measurement by toggling off outbound clicks, site search, video engagement, and file downloads. This marginally helps but does not solve the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Link Building Strategy in Utah | Freelance Website Designer for Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/link-building-strategy-utah/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/link-building-strategy-utah/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="link-building-strategy-in-utah"&gt;Link Building Strategy in Utah&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For small businesses in Utah, getting noticed online can be a challenge. As a freelance web designer, I help my clients not only with their website&amp;rsquo;s design but also with their off-page SEO. A crucial part of that is link building. Quality backlinks are like votes of confidence for your website in the eyes of Google, and they are a powerful way to increase your authority and climb the search rankings. This post will explain how link building works and why it&amp;rsquo;s a game-changer for local SEO.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mobile Website Design in Utah | Freelance Website Designer for Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/mobile-website-design-utah/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/mobile-website-design-utah/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;In today&amp;rsquo;s world, most of your customers will visit your website on a mobile device. As a freelance web designer in Utah, I specialize in creating websites for small businesses that look great and function perfectly on any screen size. A mobile-friendly website is no longer a luxury—it&amp;rsquo;s a necessity. This post will cover the three most important aspects of mobile web design to ensure your customers have a great experience, whether they&amp;rsquo;re on a phone, tablet, or desktop.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Off-Page Search Engine Optimization in Utah | Freelance Website Designer for Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/off-page-search-engine-optimization-utah/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/off-page-search-engine-optimization-utah/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;As a freelance web designer, I&amp;rsquo;m dedicated to helping small businesses in Utah succeed online. While a great website is the foundation, what happens off your website is just as important. Off-page Search Engine Optimization (SEO) is how you build authority and drive traffic to your site. In this post, we&amp;rsquo;ll explore the three pillars of effective off-page SEO and how they can bring long-term, organic growth to your business.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Shell Script for ImageMagick to Resize Images</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/shell-script-imagemagick-resize-images/</link><pubDate>Mon, 28 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/shell-script-imagemagick-resize-images/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;If you work in web publishing you often need to resize many images to be under a specific size, or of a different format, without loosing quality. This zsh script uses ImageMagick to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Convert multiple image to JPEG or a different image format such as AVIF or WebP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set the width of your images&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Resize images so that each on is under a specified size (default of 130 KB)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Organize your original images into an Originals/ folder and resized images into a Resized/ folder&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>On-Page SEO Strategy in Utah | Freelance Website Designer for Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/blog/on-page-seo-strategy-utah/</link><pubDate>Sat, 26 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/blog/on-page-seo-strategy-utah/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re a small business owner in Utah, you know how important it is to be visible to your local customers. As a freelance web designer, I specialize in helping small businesses like yours improve their online presence. A critical piece of that puzzle is on-page Search Engine Optimization (SEO). This post will walk you through the essential on-page SEO techniques that will help your website rank higher in search results and attract more customers.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>About Clear Presence | Freelance Website Designer for Utah Small Businesses</title><link>https://clearpresence.io/about/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://clearpresence.io/about/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="your-freelance-website-designer-in-utah"&gt;Your Freelance Website Designer in Utah&lt;/h1&gt;
